original: Björkström, Sven-Gösta, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 10/4/14 i Gbg av maskin-insp. Sigurd B. o. Emma Andersson. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 35, tandläk:ex. 43. Vik. i Kungsbacka 43, assist, i Stenungsund 43-44, tandläk. i Kungsbacka fr. 44. Hobbies: segl., smal-filmn.
translated: Björkström, Sven-Gösta, dentist, Gothenburg, b. April 10, 1914 in Gothenburg to machine inspector Sigurd B. and Emma Andersson. Graduated high school in Stockholm in 1935, graduated as a dentist in 1943. Worked temporarily in Kungsbacka in 1943, assistant in Stenungsund from 1943-1944, and was a dentist in Kungsbacka from 1944 onwards. Hobbies include sailing and amateur filmmaking.
